  author   = "Radhakrishnan, Periyasamy and Moirangthem, Amita and Nayak,
              Shalini S and Shukla, Anju and Mathew, Mary and Girisha, Katta M",
  abstract = "Glycogen storage disease IV (GSD IV), caused by a defect in GBE1,
              is a clinically heterogeneous disorder. A classical hepatic form
              and a neuromuscular form have been described. The severe
              neuromuscular form presents as a fetal akinesia deformation
