               insomnia 8 (26\%); dizziness 7 (23\%); dry mouth 7 (23\%);
               depressed consciousness 5 (16\%); nausea 4 (13\%). Conclusions:
               Results show improvement across cognitive, mood, and fatigue
               outcome measures. Modafinil was generally well tolerated, with a
               low incidence of adverse events. Greatest improvements in
               outcomes were observed 8 wks after baseline. Neurobehavioral and
